{"tid":429975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普暗示採軍事行動","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T14:59:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"892d1e5e1f99de5fa3ce5798ef5791a386636b30","tid":429975,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176646&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176646%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&d=hAoLjnH3VPVtREvRwMsKRJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ac2c2ccf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20176646%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171009&h=2121499e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20176646&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171009</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普暗示採軍事行動<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=a86f3e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子母彈內有大量鎳和碳纖維絲。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普繼續向北韓發出強硬措詞，前日在推特發文指「歷屆總統和政府跟北韓談了足足25年，簽過多份協議，錢也花了一大筆&hellip;&hellip;但全部不成功，油墨還未乾透對方便毀約，把美國談判代表當作儍瓜。很遺憾，只有一件事才會奏效。」雖然無解釋是甚麼事，但分析相信一直不排除動武的他，是暗示採取軍事行動。<br />\n<br />\n南韓研斷電彈襲核彈基地<br />\n<br />\n面對北韓威脅會用導彈射向關島周邊水域，特朗普曾揚言要徹底摧毀對方。早前，美國國務卿蒂勒森訪華尋求北京居中斡旋，豈料當他回國後，特朗普大潑冷水，推文指美國尋求同北韓對話「是浪費時間」。俄羅斯一名國會議員上周五透露，北韓正準備試射一枚可達美國西岸的遠程導彈。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮半島局勢陰霾不定，南韓一方面極力避免韓戰重啟，另方面也做好最壞打算，修飭武備，南韓國防科學研究所已開發出斷電炸彈，若戰時投擲在北韓發電廠上空引爆，其高傳導性的鎳和碳纖維一旦接觸到電網便會造成短路，切斷其供電，可兵不血刃便癱瘓對方的核彈基地至少12個小時。 <br />\n<br />\n法新社/中央社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/a1402b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2Fa1402b.gif&h=26e039cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t金正恩妹任政治局候補委員　躋權力核心<br />\n國際新聞 14小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t北韓外交官奇招賺外滙使館賣牛肉　搞派對<br />\n國際新聞 14小時前"},{"pid":"1e3573f07b9a7325268d801d2bdd0be330f9e024","tid":429975,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"on9仔原來你係呢個原因port我?<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nuj30lfo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnuj30lfo&h=8649a17b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a40f9823aacf6fe5185df15ccd15e05c1905d702","tid":429975,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"聽了幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}